			</image>
			<staticText>
				<reportElement positionType="Float" x="0" y="0" width="545" height="103" uuid="e7249551-90eb-4d06-a59c-36cc1332adcd"/>
				<textElement textAlignment="Center" verticalAlignment="Middle" markup="html">
					<font size="14" isPdfEmbedded="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[<font size='4' color='#004280'><b>REPORT</b></font><br><font size='2' color='#004280'>SELF-ASSESSMENT SURVEY<br><font size='1' color='#004280'>Snap Frozen - Part 1: Isolated RNA (Version 2)</font>]]></text>
			</staticText>
		</band>
	</pageHeader>
	<detail>
		<band height="25" splitType="Prevent">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement x="25" y="0" width="272" height="25" uuid="24aa5b0b-a537-4019-b850-250a9c7b6517"/>
				<textElement verticalAlignment="Top" markup="html">
					<font size="12" pdfFontName="net/sf/jasperreports/fonts/dejavu/DejaVuSerif-Bold.ttf" isPdfEmbedded="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[Record ID]]></text>
			</staticText>
			<textField isStretchWithOverflow="true">
				<reportElement x="322" y="0" width="248" height="25" uuid="65c705b7-2aad-4b3a-900e-543a167fb5d8"/>
				<textElement textAlignment="Right" verticalAlignment="Middle" markup="html">
					<font size="12" pdfFontName="net/sf/jasperreports/fonts/dejavu/DejaVuSerif-Bold.ttf" isPdfEmbedded="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<textFieldExpression><![CDATA[$F{record_id}+"<br>"]]></textFieldExpression>
			</textField>
		</band>
		<band height="90">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement positionType="Float" x="25" y="0" width="545" height="90" uuid="c6228395-1d61-4801-af69-ad5a2c2119b0"/>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified" verticalAlignment="Middle" markup="html">
					<font size="12" pdfFontName="net/sf/jasperreports/fonts/dejavu/DejaVuSerif-Italic.ttf" isPdfEmbedded="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[Molecule profiles can change during primary sample collection, which is why transport, storage and processing may influence research results. Standardising the entire process from sample collection to the selection of appropriate analysis methods is therefore crucial. ]]></text>
			</staticText>
		</band>
		<band height="105">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement positionType="Float" x="25" y="0" width="545" height="105" uuid="0573a9e6-66e8-478f-8901-987c86269260"/>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified" verticalAlignment="Middle" markup="html">
					<font size="12" pdfFontName="net/sf/jasperreports/fonts/dejavu/DejaVuSerif-Italic.ttf" isPdfEmbedded="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[The European Committee for Standardisation (CEN) published Technical Specifications to determine influencing factors and provide recommendations for the handling, documentation and processing of  frozen tissue specimens intended for RNA analysis (CEN/TS 16826-1:2015 E, Molecular in vitro diagnostic examinations for snap frozen tissue - Part 1: Isolated  RNA). For further details, please visit the <a href="https://standards.cen.eu/dyn/www/f?p=204:110:0::::FSP_PROJECT:41033&cs=17D5B1C84523ECF122A5B0890BB6C3A98" style="color:#004280" target="_blank">CEN website</a>. ]]></text>
			</staticText>
		</band>
		<band height="60">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement positionType="Float" x="25" y="0" width="545" height="60" uuid="5027b285-edb3-4ed6-bf4d-5d46ea6af71c"/>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified" verticalAlignment="Middle" markup="html">
					<font size="12" pdfFontName="net/sf/jasperreports/fonts/dejavu/DejaVuSerif-Italic.ttf" isPdfEmbedded="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[This Self-Assessment Survey will help you to assess and improve your sample processing.]]></text>
			</staticText>
		</band>
		<band height="90">
			<staticText>
				<reportElement positionType="Float" x="25" y="0" width="545" height="90" uuid="227d1b93-d440-4382-9ed1-0ce11b10cf23"/>
				<textElement textAlignment="Justified" verticalAlignment="Middle" markup="html">
					<font size="12" pdfFontName="net/sf/jasperreports/fonts/dejavu/DejaVuSerif-Italic.ttf" isPdfEmbedded="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[The questions are colour-coded. <font color="#ec6607">Orange</font> criteria are <font color="#ec6607">'shall'</font> criteria, i.e. meeting them is a requirement. <font color="#004280">Blue</font> criteria are <font color="#004280"> 'should'</font> criteria, i.e. meeting them is recommended. Making true and accurate statements will help you get genuine feedback on your sample collection procedures and, as a result, improve certain processes in the future.]]></text>
			</staticText>
		</band>
